    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>spicy chorizo spaghetti</strong> topped with the<strong> grilled cherry tomatoes</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and garnish with a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
